Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The Moral Majority
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wtsq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Feb 1982
Jane Fonda and Barry Goldwater make unlikely appearance together in bid to silence the 'Moral Majority'. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less